[2026-06-21 00:00:00] ouroboros: Fixed Emacs freezing issue with execute_code_local and delegate tools. Root cause: Emacs threads are cooperative (non-preemptive), and `shell-command-to-string` uses `call-process` which blocks the entire Emacs process at C level. Refactored to use `make-process` + `accept-process-output` async pattern. Added 3600s default timeout. Fixed shell path: container uses busybox `/bin/sh` not `/bin/bash`.
